Valerie Jackson suffers Netherton's syndrome - a rare congenital skin disease . 
  Four-year-old RJ Jackson is one of just 70 people in the world who suffers the illness . 
  His skin appears red and scaly and he has to be covered in creams to prevent it drying out . 
  While out shopping with her son she was reported to police for child abuse . 
  A member of the public thought she was abusing her son . 
  Mrs Jackson said she was accused of scalding her son because of the condition . 
  She said she has been treated like an outcast because of her son's illness . 
 